  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aimed to determine the impact of providing chest physiotherapy on the duration of
      mechanical ventilation, intensive care length of stay, intensive care and hospital mortality
      in mechanically ventilated patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
